description:
MOTIVATED SELLER!!!  Ask about rental permit!
Discover this exciting new listing that embodies both luxury and investment potential! This spacious condo features an open floor plan, making it the perfect retreat or investment opportunity. The highlight of this property is the transferable rental permit, a rare find with an active tenant in place. With a 3-4 year waiting list for this permit, new owners can enjoy immediate rental income!

Relax in natural light thanks to the impressive floor-to-ceiling windows that frame picturesque views. The condo offers a generous walk-in closet, an additional bedroom closet, and a pantry, ensuring ample storage and organization.

Located in a pet-friendly community with 24-hour concierge service, this property offers comfort and convenience. Steps from Broadway, you’ll be surrounded by an array of vibrant restaurants and nightlife. Plus, it's just a 2-minute walk to Bridgestone Arena and within walking distance to Titans Stadium, making it an unbeatable location for city living! With the new Riverside development and new Titans Stadium being built next door, this makes the perfect investment 

Whether you’re looking for your next investment property or a spacious new home in a thriving city, this condo is a rare opportunity not to be missed.
